high_descs: Head to the sofa in front.
Pick up the ladle from the couch.
Turn left to reach the cabinet above the microwave.
Put the ladle in the cabinet.
Turn around and head out of the kitchen and reach the countertop next to the sink.
Pick up the ladle from the counter.
Head back to the cabinet above the microwave.
Put the ladle in the cabinet with the other spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put two ladles in the kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Move across the room and go to a nearby sofa.
Pick up the ladle from the couch.
Turn around and walk towards the cabinet.
Put the ladle inside the kitchen cabinet which is above the microwave.
Turn around and go to the kitchen countertop.
Pick up the ladle from the kitchen tabletop.
Turn your left and walk to another side of the kitchen cabinet.
Put the ladle inside the kitchen cabinet which is above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the two ladles into the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the ladle from the couch.
Turn around and go near the kitchen cabinet.
Put the ladle on the kitchen cabinet.
Turn around and go near the countertop.
Take another ladle from the table.
Turn around and go near the kitchen cabinet.
Put the ladle on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Collect the ladle and placed it on the kitchen cabinet.
